  • Constructor Details

    • Transaction

      public Transaction(int number, int index, int gasLimit, long gasPrice, String fromAdr, String toAdr)
      Constructs a Transaction object and initializes its number, index, gasLimit, gasPrice, fromAdr, and toAdr.
      Parameters:
      number - The number that identifies the transaction
      index - The index of the transaction
      gasLimit - The maximum amount of work you're estimating a validator will do on a particular transaction.
      gasPrice - The price per unit of work done
      fromAdr - The original location of the transaction
      toAdr - Where the transaction went from the original location
